title: Never got my Garen/Ashe chest
body: My account is now level 7 and I have not gotten my free chest that gives you Ashe and Garen. My account has been level 5 for a while now so i should have gotten it by now.

replies.body: Sometimes it can take awhile for those to be added to your account. Try refreshing your client if you haven't in awhile and let me know if you see it yet!
